Package: simpriord
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Prior Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mackson Ncube
Maintainer: Mackson Ncube <macksonncube@gmail.com>
Description: Package to explore how data used as prior distribution can bias
    results from a Bayesian model.  The package includes functions to streamline
    building data sets and running brms models.
